articles.title: Uday Saharan's reaction to taking Rohit's ‘revenge’ in U19 WC final vs Australia - Hindustan Times
articles.description: India will meet Australia in the U19 World Cup final. Before that, India captain Uday Saharan was asked about taking the senior team's ‘revenge’. | Cricket
